import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz';
import Timeline from './index';
import Quiet from '../Quiet';

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"timeline"}}>{`Timeline`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Timelines are good to illustrate a connected set of events that have happened or are planned to happen.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"standard"}}>{`Standard`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={0} __code={'<Timeline>\n  <Timeline.Item>Nothing</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Big Bang</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Galaxies go everywhere</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Solar systems form</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Earth appears</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Human infestation occurs!</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item last>\n    All this has happened before, and will happen again\n  </Timeline.Item>\n</Timeline>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Timeline,Quiet}}>
    <Timeline>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Nothing
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Big Bang
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Galaxies go everywhere
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Solar systems form
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Earth appears
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Human infestation occurs!
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item last>
            All this has happened before, and will happen again
        </Timeline.Item>
    </Timeline>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"colours"}}>{`Colours`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={1} __code={'<Timeline>\n  <Timeline.Item>Nothing</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"brand\">Big Bang</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"info\">Galaxies go everywhere</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"warning\">Solar systems form</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"success\">Earth appears</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"error\">Human infestation occurs!</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item last>\n    All this has happened before, and will happen again\n  </Timeline.Item>\n</Timeline>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Timeline,Quiet}}>
    <Timeline>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Nothing
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="brand">
            Big Bang
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="info">
            Galaxies go everywhere
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="warning">
            Solar systems form
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="success">
            Earth appears
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="error">
            Human infestation occurs!
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item last>
            All this has happened before, and will happen again
        </Timeline.Item>
    </Timeline>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"loading-last-item"}}>{`Loading last item`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Use the `}<MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`loading`}</MDXTag>{` prop on both the `}<MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="p">{`Timeline`}</MDXTag>{` and `}<MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="p">{`Timeline.Item`}</MDXTag>{` components to indicate the last item hasn't happened yet.`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={2} __code={'<Timeline loading>\n  <Timeline.Item>Nothing</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Big Bang</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Galaxies go everywhere</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Solar systems form</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Earth appears</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item>Human infestation occurs!</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item last>\n    All this has happened before, and will happen again\n  </Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item loading>...Evolution</Timeline.Item>\n</Timeline>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Timeline,Quiet}}>
    <Timeline loading>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Nothing
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Big Bang
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Galaxies go everywhere
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Solar systems form
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Earth appears
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Human infestation occurs!
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item last>
            All this has happened before, and will happen again
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item loading>
            ...Evolution
        </Timeline.Item>
    </Timeline>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"alternating-items"}}>{`Alternating items`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Use the `}<MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`left`}</MDXTag>{` prop on a `}<MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="p">{`Timeline.Item`}</MDXTag>{` to put it on the left side of the Timeline.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Make sure to put the `}<MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`alternate`}</MDXTag>{` prop on the `}<MDXTag name="em" components={components} parentName="p">{`Timeline`}</MDXTag>{` as well.`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={3} __code={'<Timeline loading alternate>\n  <Timeline.Item>Nothing</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"brand\">Big Bang</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"info\" left>\n    Galaxies go everywhere\n  </Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"warning\">Solar systems form</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"success\" left>\n    Earth appears\n  </Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item type=\"error\">Human infestation occurs!</Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item last left>\n    All this has happened before, and will happen again\n  </Timeline.Item>\n  <Timeline.Item loading>...Evolution</Timeline.Item>\n</Timeline>'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Timeline,Quiet}}>
    <Timeline loading alternate>
        <Timeline.Item>
            Nothing
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="brand">
            Big Bang
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="info" left>
            Galaxies go everywhere
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="warning">
            Solar systems form
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="success" left>
            Earth appears
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item type="error">
            Human infestation occurs!
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item last left>
            All this has happened before, and will happen again
        </Timeline.Item>
        <Timeline.Item loading>
            ...Evolution
        </Timeline.Item>
    </Timeline>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"timeline-1"}}>{`Timeline`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Timeline} />
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"timelineitem"}}>{`Timeline.Item`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Timeline.Item} />
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
